The paper deals with graph theory and algorithms related to minimum degree, which are topics commonly found in the sub-categories of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem and provides exact algorithms, which are relevant to Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), and Graph Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories.
